title: The Bucks Beat the Hawks and Advance to the NBA Finals | Postgame
description:
Kevin O'Connor and J. Kyle Mann rejoin after Game 6 in Atlanta to discuss Milwaukee's victory over the Hawks and advancing to the Finals against the Suns. They discuss what key elements took the Bucks to victory, along with what to look forward to in the Finals when the two teams battle it out.
Hosts: Kevin O'Connor and J. Kyle Mann
Producer: Steve Ahlman
